<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-observa-diagramas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The diagrams have a lot of the same numbers.</li>
      <li>The first diagram shows 20 and the others show four 5s.</li>
      <li>The total is missing in all the diagrams.</li>
      <li>The first diagram shows addition.</li>
      <li>The second diagram shows multiplication.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>What is the total in each diagram?</li>
      <li>What operation does the last diagram show?</li>
      <li>Does the last diagram show multiplication and addition?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


